---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro"
import LinkButton from "../components/LinkButton.astro"
import InfoCard from "../components/InfoCard.astro"

import logo from "../assets/knowy.svg"
---

<Layout>
	<Navbar />

	<main class="h-auto w-full">
		<section class="grid h-3/5 grid-cols-1 bg-green-200 p-12 font-sans md:grid-cols-2">
			<div data-label="Intro" class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 text-center">
				<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-800">¡Aprende los conceptos de programación a tu ritmo!</h1>
				<p class="text-lg text-green-900">Cursos interactivos, retos y aprendizaje personalizado.</p>

				<div class="mt-4 flex flex-row items-center justify-end gap-2">
					<LinkButton href="#" variant="primary">Inicio Sesión</LinkButton>
					<LinkButton href="#" variant="secondary">Registrarse</LinkButton>
				</div>
			</div>
			<a data-label="Logo" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 not-md:hidden">
				<img src={logo.src} alt="Logo" width={logo.width} height={logo.height} />
			</a>
		</section>

		<section
			class="flex flex-row items-center justify-center gap-10 overflow-hidden bg-green-500 p-3 font-sans text-lg font-bold text-white"
		>
			<span>Java</span>
			<span>JavaScript</span>
			<span>TypeScript</span>
			<span>Ruby</span>
			<span>C#</span>
			<span>SQL</span>
			<span>Python</span>
		</section>

		<section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-8 py-6">
			<h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-medium">Funcionalidades</h2>

			<div class="flex w-full flex-row flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
				<InfoCard title="Aprendizaje Personalizado">
					<svg slot="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="50" height="50" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path
							class="fill-green-500"
							d="M12 3L1 9l4 2.18v6L12 21l7-3.82v-6l2-1.09V17h2V9zm6.82 6L12 12.72L5.18 9L12 5.28zM17 16l-5 2.72L7 16v-3.73L12 15l5-2.73z"
						></path>
					</svg>
					Adapta el contenido y los ejercicios según tu ritmo y nivel de experiencia. Recibe recomendaciones inteligentes
					para mejorar tus habilidades día a día.
				</InfoCard>

				<InfoCard title="Desarrollo Open Source">
					<svg slot="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="45" height="45" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
						<path
							class="fill-green-500"
							d="M15.5 1.125C7.278 1.125.59 7.815.59 16.035c0 6.263 3.88 11.635 9.36 13.84l3.64-9.076a5.131 5.131 0 1 1 3.818-.001l3.64 9.075c5.48-2.206 9.36-7.578 9.36-13.84c.002-8.22-6.687-14.91-14.908-14.91z"
						></path>
					</svg>
					Creemos en la colaboración y la transparencia. Este proyecto es open source, creado por y para la comunidad.
					¡Explora el código y deja tu huella!
				</InfoCard>

				<InfoCard title="Contenido Colaborativo">
					<svg slot="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="45" height="45" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path
							class="fill-none stroke-green-500 stroke-2"
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							d="M7 15h10v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H9a2 2 0 0 1-2-2zm5-6a6 6 0 0 0-6-6H3v2a6 6 0 0 0 6 6h3m0 0a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h3v1a6 6 0 0 1-6 6h-3m0 3V9"
						></path>
					</svg>
					Los cursos pueden ser creados por profesores y miembros de la comunidad, fomentando el intercambio de
					conocimiento y experiencias reales.
				</InfoCard>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 p-6">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-medium">Últimas Novedades</h2>

			<div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-white p-10 shadow-sm shadow-zinc-200">
				<ol class="relative border-s border-gray-200">
					<li class="ms-6">
						<span
							class="absolute -start-3 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-100 ring-8 ring-white"
						>
							<svg
								class="h-2.5 w-2.5 text-green-800"
								aria-hidden="true"
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
								fill="currentColor"
								viewBox="0 0 20 20"
							>
								<path
									d="M20 4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1h-3V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H6V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2h20V4ZM0 18a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8H0v10Zm5-8h10a1 1 0 0 1 0 2H5a1 1 0 0 1 0-2Z"
								>
								</path>
							</svg>
						</span>
						<h3 class="mb-1 flex items-center text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
							Flowbite Application UI v2.0.0 <span
								class="ms-3 me-2 rounded-sm bg-green-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-medium text-green-800"
							>
								Latest
							</span>
						</h3>
						<time class="mb-2 block text-sm leading-none font-normal text-gray-400">
							Released on January 13th, 2022
						</time>
						<p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-500">
							Get access to over 20+ pages including a dashboard layout, charts, kanban board, calendar,
							and pre-order E-commerce & Marketing pages.
						</p>
						<a
							href="#"
							class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 hover:text-green-700 focus:z-10 focus:text-green-700 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-100 focus:outline-none"
						>
							<svg
								class="me-2.5 h-3.5 w-3.5"
								aria-hidden="true"
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
								fill="currentColor"
								viewBox="0 0 20 20"
							>
								<path
									d="M14.707 7.793a1 1 0 0 0-1.414 0L11 10.086V1.5a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v8.586L6.707 7.793a1 1 0 1 0-1.414 1.414l4 4a1 1 0 0 0 1.416 0l4-4a1 1 0 0 0-.002-1.414Z"
								>
								</path>
								<path
									d="M18 12h-2.55l-2.975 2.975a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0L4.55 12H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2Zm-3 5a1 1 0 1 1 0-2 1 1 0 0 1 0 2Z"
								>
								</path>
							</svg>
							Download ZIP
						</a>
					</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

